								</th>
								<th style="text-align: center;font-weight: bold;">
									<span>
										Weight of Immersion in water after 30 Minutes (kg)	
									</span>
								</th>
								<th style="text-align: center;font-weight: bold;">
									<span>
										Water Absorption  %	
									</span>
								</th>
								<th style="text-align: center;font-weight: bold;">	 
